  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">The focus of this repetition is on these sentences:</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Sentence 1 - びょういんの　せんせいは　なんと　いいましたか。= What did the doctor at the hospital say?</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Sentence 2 - かぜだと　いいました。= He/she said it&#39;s just a cold.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">How to use this lesson - When the repeat message shows and the video pauses, please repeat the sentence you have just heard. Keep practising until you can repeat perfectly!</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/brq0rpcobr2ovlios3g0\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D36 L1 R1.mp4 - 00:12\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span></span></p></div>",
